full_text:

Join us on FB Live: https://t.co/iBgRFRJsNX

#DontMessWithUSPS

- Text 838255

I’m proud to sign onto legislation to recognize #Juneteenth as a national holiday.

25th time’s a charm ⬇️

full_text:
The #CARESAct makes sure that self-employed workers, contractors, and gig economy workers affected by #COVID19 can receive unemployment benefits.

Head to https://t.co/ldj4I110Z3 to file, & feel free to contact my office if you need assistance or have any questions: 702-963-9336

-$350 billion in grants and forgivable loans
-$10 billion for @SBAgov emergency loans for small businesses
-$17 billion for @SBAgov to cover 6 months of payments for small businesses with existing SBA loans

full_text:
The #CARESAct sends direct cash assistance of $1,200 to individuals and $2,400 to working families. 

A one-time payment is helpful, but it’s not enough, which is why we expanded unemployment benefits to $600 more per month to cover salaries for 4 months for the average American.

✅Connect with friends & family
✅Make time for hobbies

#selfcarematters

✅Free testing 
✅Food assistance 
✅Paid & family leave 
✅health care worker protections 

The fight’s not over.
